  "text": "Staining of HS and CS. As previously described [CITATION_1] , RFPEC monolayers were fixed with 2% paraformaldehyde/0.1% glutaraldehyde, blocked with 2% goat serum (GS; Invitrogen), stained with HS mouse monoclonal antibody (1:100; 10E4 epitope, AMS Biotechnology) and biotinylated Griffonia (Bandeiraea) Simplicifolia Lectin II (GSL II; 100 g/cm 2 in ϫ1 DPBS without calcium and magnesium; Vector Labs), and then visualized with Alexa Fluor 488 goat antimouse antibody (1:300; Molecular Probes) and Alexa Fluor 488 anti-Biotin (1:100 in ϫ1 DPBS, Jackson ImmunoResearch Lab), respectively.",
